34 (1) year that shows the customer's name, location of delivery, and
35 quantity sold. Subject to subsection (g), a wine retailer also may
36 prepare and package wine in qualified containers for sale and delivery
37 to a customer on the licensed premises for consumption off the licensed
38 premises.
